name: Open Compliance Issues
query:
SELECT
	name as "Issue:Link/Issue:100",
	raised_on "Raised on:Date:100", 
	subject "Subject::350",
	business_line "Category::120",
	status "Status::100", 
	creation "Created on:Date:100"
FROM
	`tabIssue`
WHERE
	status in ("Open") and 
	business_line in ("Compliance","Accounts")
